{{>layout/header}}

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/evaluate.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nav2.css">
</head>
<body>
<!-- 네브바 -->
<nav class="header">
    <div class="navbar_logo">
        <i class="fas fa-cloud-sun" id="logo"></i>
        <a class="nav_title" href="/">WeatherWear</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="navbar_menu">
        <li><a href="/users/save-wear">옷차림저장</a></li>
        <li><a href="/users/eval-wear" class="active">평가하기</a></li>
        <li><a href="/logout">로그아웃</a></li> <!--페이지없이 js로처리-->
    </ul>
    <ul class="navbar_icons">
        <li><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></li>
        <li><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></li>
    </ul>
</nav>
<!--네브바-->
<div>
    <h1>지난 옷차림은 어땠나요?</h1>
</div>
<div class="container">
    <h2>해당 날씨에 입으신 지난 옷차림은 어떠셨나요?</h2>
    <p>평가를 해주시면, 정확한 추천에 도움이 됩니다:)</p>
    <p>❌를 선택하시면, 앞으로의 평가항목에서 제외됩니다.</p>

    {{#wears}}
    <div class="eval">
        <div class="eval-date">
            <div class="eval-date-2">
                <span class="eval-date-date">{{wear_date}}</span>
                <span class="eval-date-temp">{{temp_code}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="wear_code">{{wear_code}}</div>
        <div class="eval-clothes">
            <img class="outerImg" src="" alt="OUTER">
            <img class="topImg" src="" alt="TOP">
            <img class="bottomImg" src="" alt="BOTTOM">
        </div>
        <div class="eval-btn">
            <span class="eval-wear-no hidden">{{wear_no}}</span>
            <button id="hot-btn" class="hot-btn">더워요</button>
            <button id="warm-btn" class="warm-btn">적절해요</button>
            <button id="cold-btn" class="cold-btn">추워요</button>
            <button id="del-btn">❌</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{/wears}}
</div>
<script src="/js/eval.js"></script>
{{>layout/footer}}